8002	  underlying coproduct \(\coprod_{j \in I} U_j\), lifted to the slice since the forgetful functor
8003	  \(\operatorname{Over} X \to \operatorname{Scheme}\) reflects the required equalities.
8004	  Comparing with the standard coproduct in \(\operatorname{Over} X\) yields the asserted isomorphism.
8005	\end{proof}
